WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
A hand reaches out from the coffin, startling Zhang Peizan.

2
00:00:09.102 --> 00:00:11.800
A female ghost sits up from the coffin.

3
00:00:14.072 --> 00:00:20.000
Zhang Peizan stumbles backward and falls; the ghost advances, her face hidden in darkness.

4
00:00:33.475 --> 00:00:36.300
Her ghostly white face is suddenly revealed.

5
00:00:49.900 --> 00:00:52.300
Zhang kneels as the ghost circles him.

6
00:00:56.509 --> 00:01:02.000
The door slams shut, sealing Zhang inside.

7
00:01:59.042 --> 00:02:03.700
Judge Bao appears above; Qianjin removes her disguise. Zhang collapses.
